channel.title: Some kind of music
channel.description:
I'm not going to categorize this because there WILL be a debate over it.
My best friend has a new band and they're just getting started. This was their first show so I filmed it for them.
Instead of linking you to each video I shot of them, just go here. It's the newest post at the top of the page and it's the four videos. Enjoy them in their HD + Youtube artifacted goodness.
http://somethingtohide.info/
PS: IMO I think it's like Underoath meets Angels&Airwaves meets typical local band.
